        "text": "FROM : L. B. Nichols\nSUBJECT: INFORMATION CONCERNING\nFLYING DISCS\nBUREAU FILE 62-83894, Serials 80, 284, and 225\nDuring my absence, at 11:50 A.M. today,\nin the office of Drew Pearson, called and talked with"
      },
